Revision history for Texinfo::Menus

1.03   2013-09-28
	- use 'our' instead of 'use vars'

1.02   2010-12-07
	- Handle @documentencoding (so menus line up properly in UTF-8)
	- Require Perl 5.8.0

1.01   2007-06-09
	- added Pod coverage test
	- updated my email address
	- cleaned up documentation & build process
	- no functional changes

1.00   2007-02-03
	- Initial public release
